{"tid":2028251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美政界提議取消香港獨立關稅區","createTime":"2020-05-21T17:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T17:09:29.000Z","uid":184679,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"96c572d94bfd59d812da44be79b764b2b40fdb25","tid":2028251,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:05:34.000Z","msg":"美國國務卿龐皮歐近期多次針對香港事務發聲表示，留意到中國政府威脅干涉美國駐港記者的工作，揚言任何侵犯香港自治的決定，都會影響美國對香港地位的評估。美國政界也有聲音提出，直接取消香港獨立關稅區地位...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200518/SFRKVFRDG2ALSB3IPFBT5PJDWQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200518%2FSFRKVFRDG2ALSB3IPFBT5PJDWQ%2F&d=ppuFFh6piFuOrul45s7BzQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=ae36f368\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200518%2FSFRKVFRDG2ALSB3IPFBT5PJDWQ%2F&h=47002b9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200518/SFRKVFRDG2ALSB3IPFBT5PJDWQ/</a>"},{"pid":"815b694e4b48197796d8b974d9ed7dbbd2f233b4","tid":2028251,"uid":41458,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:06:35.000Z","msg":"post 完舊聞未？同一篇新聞post 足幾日,開幾廿個post"},{"pid":"ec632b588de447f8f9d759a0939a96746f91fe13","tid":2028251,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:06:41.000Z","msg":"我地要同共產黨對賭香港對世界經濟嘅影響力<br />\n賭美國守香港嘅決心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">本來佢地日日扮一國兩制<br />\n搞個假法治搵黑警濫捕<br />\n搵紅官亂判<br />\n班鬼佬都無乜位入香港</span><br />\n<br />\n而家支共直接插旗撕破埋假面具<br />\n今次係我地香港人最後生機<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">成件串埋港共 黑警 紅官 賣港狗<br />\n支那亂港<br />\n一國一制共產黨亂港<br />\n<br />\n到時外國想淨係制裁班共狗又好<br />\n成個香港制裁都好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</span></span><br />\n我地都無得輸<br />\n因為無野差得過跟住落嚟落入支那手<br />\n變新疆2.0"},{"pid":"66d0b98c20993c3f9dc7e9ea21cd19d13c68be87","tid":2028251,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"815b694e4b481